1
00:00:00,111 --> 00:00:01,951
A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES

2
00:01:22,391 --> 00:01:27,043
METEOR GARDEN

3
00:01:27,111 --> 00:01:30,031
EPISODE 30

4
00:01:46,791 --> 00:01:47,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Miss Caina.</b></font>

5
00:01:49,551 --> 00:01:50,471
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How are you doing?</b></font>

6
00:01:52,671 --> 00:01:53,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm doing fine.</b></font>

7
00:01:57,111 --> 00:01:58,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Actually...</b></font>

8
00:01:58,671 --> 00:02:00,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop if you're not fine.</b></font>

9
00:02:06,311 --> 00:02:07,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Here.</b></font>

10
00:02:07,711 --> 00:02:09,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'll order a cocktail for you today.</b></font>

11
00:02:10,111 --> 00:02:10,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Wei Xun.</b></font>

12
00:02:12,951 --> 00:02:14,191
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I want to order</b></font>

13
00:02:16,431 --> 00:02:17,631
<font color="#ffff00"><b>"Goodbye Old Place."</b></font>

14
00:02:18,711 --> 00:02:20,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I want it sour, sweet, bitter and spicy.</b></font>

15
00:02:20,991 --> 00:02:21,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Everything in it.</b></font>

16
00:02:22,951 --> 00:02:23,911
<font color="#ffff00"><b>One for each of us.</b></font>

17
00:02:23,991 --> 00:02:24,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right.</b></font>

18
00:02:25,671 --> 00:02:26,871
<font color="#ffff00"><b>"Goodbye Old Place"?</b></font>

19
00:02:28,791 --> 00:02:29,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What does that mean?</b></font>

20
00:02:30,751 --> 00:02:32,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are we not coming here again?</b></font>

21
00:02:32,911 --> 00:02:33,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No, we're not.</b></font>

22
00:02:34,791 --> 00:02:35,631
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Caina.</b></font>

23
00:02:36,391 --> 00:02:38,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you remember what I told you?</b></font>

24
00:02:39,311 --> 00:02:40,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Meeting me</b></font>

25
00:02:40,871 --> 00:02:42,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>is the beginning of your happiness.</b></font>

26
00:02:43,431 --> 00:02:44,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Today,</b></font>

27
00:02:46,471 --> 00:02:48,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I want to officially start this happiness.</b></font>

28
00:02:49,311 --> 00:02:50,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you're not coming back,</b></font>

29
00:02:52,671 --> 00:02:53,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b>it'd be</b></font>

30
00:02:54,231 --> 00:02:55,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>my treat today.</b></font>

31
00:02:55,751 --> 00:02:57,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>All right. Cheers.</b></font>

32
00:02:57,631 --> 00:02:58,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Here.</b></font>

33
00:03:10,191 --> 00:03:11,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The taste is horrible.</b></font>

34
00:03:13,431 --> 00:03:15,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If we had this the first time,</b></font>

35
00:03:16,791 --> 00:03:18,911
<font color="#ffff00"><b>maybe we wouldn't have met
the second time.</b></font>

36
00:03:20,671 --> 00:03:21,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Sometimes,</b></font>

37
00:03:22,151 --> 00:03:23,871
<font color="#ffff00"><b>we cannot tell the outcome beforehand.</b></font>

38
00:03:25,911 --> 00:03:27,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because if we did,</b></font>

39
00:03:28,911 --> 00:03:30,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b>then we'd have no courage to do it.</b></font>

40
00:03:35,351 --> 00:03:36,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But if we don't,</b></font>

41
00:03:37,911 --> 00:03:39,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>how would we know the outcome?</b></font>

42
00:03:55,191 --> 00:03:56,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Since we got to know each other,</b></font>

43
00:03:57,351 --> 00:03:58,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>this is the first time</b></font>

44
00:03:58,471 --> 00:04:01,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you didn't get drunk
after having one glass.</b></font>

45
00:04:02,111 --> 00:04:03,271
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because you said</b></font>

46
00:04:04,351 --> 00:04:06,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>we won't go to that old place again.</b></font>

47
00:04:07,991 --> 00:04:10,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't want to face you
in a confused state.</b></font>

48
00:04:11,031 --> 00:04:13,271
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Love is confusing.</b></font>

49
00:04:14,471 --> 00:04:15,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't want to be too sober today.</b></font>

50
00:04:16,831 --> 00:04:17,911
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Or else, I won't be able</b></font>

51
00:04:18,711 --> 00:04:19,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>to tell you what I want.</b></font>

52
00:04:23,231 --> 00:04:24,471
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You have something to tell me?</b></font>

53
00:04:25,431 --> 00:04:27,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-What a coincidence. I--
-Don't say it yet.</b></font>

54
00:04:28,431 --> 00:04:29,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Follow me.</b></font>

55
00:04:33,431 --> 00:04:35,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Today will also be</b></font>

56
00:04:35,631 --> 00:04:37,031
<font color="#ffff00"><b>a very,</b></font>

57
00:04:37,111 --> 00:04:37,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>very good day.</b></font>

58
00:04:51,191 --> 00:04:53,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are we in my backyard?</b></font>

59
00:04:54,151 --> 00:04:55,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I have a gift for you.</b></font>

60
00:04:55,871 --> 00:04:56,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What?</b></font>

61
00:04:57,191 --> 00:04:58,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A gift for me again?</b></font>

62
00:04:58,951 --> 00:05:00,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's keep walking. You'll see it.</b></font>

63
00:05:02,831 --> 00:05:04,031
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Meizuo, wait.</b></font>

64
00:05:04,671 --> 00:05:06,191
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you so nice to me?</b></font>

65
00:05:07,471 --> 00:05:08,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because you're worth it.</b></font>

66
00:05:10,551 --> 00:05:12,631
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not as perfect as you think.</b></font>

67
00:05:15,111 --> 00:05:17,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I never thought that you are.</b></font>

68
00:05:17,631 --> 00:05:18,711
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Because you're you,</b></font>

69
00:05:19,591 --> 00:05:20,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you deserve to be loved.</b></font>

70
00:05:21,551 --> 00:05:22,871
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Just keep walking</b></font>

71
00:05:23,311 --> 00:05:24,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and you'll see</b></font>

72
00:05:24,671 --> 00:05:26,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b>where your happiness lies.</b></font>

73
00:05:29,031 --> 00:05:30,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No, Meizuo.</b></font>

74
00:05:30,791 --> 00:05:31,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I really can't.</b></font>

75
00:05:32,271 --> 00:05:34,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm moved by everything you do.</b></font>

76
00:05:35,791 --> 00:05:37,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But if I go forward,</b></font>

77
00:05:38,111 --> 00:05:39,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'd really hurt you.</b></font>

78
00:05:41,271 --> 00:05:42,271
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You won't.</b></font>

79
00:05:42,871 --> 00:05:45,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Every single day will be precious.</b></font>

80
00:05:46,391 --> 00:05:47,471
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Every single day,</b></font>

81
00:05:47,871 --> 00:05:49,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'd make you smile.</b></font>

82
00:05:50,591 --> 00:05:52,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is my promise to you.</b></font>

83
00:05:52,991 --> 00:05:53,871
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Trust me.</b></font>

84
00:05:54,311 --> 00:05:55,271
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Follow me.</b></font>

85
00:06:28,951 --> 00:06:30,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is...</b></font>

86
00:06:30,911 --> 00:06:32,711
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This is Ye Mingchuan's gift for you.</b></font>

87
00:06:34,791 --> 00:06:35,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He said</b></font>

88
00:06:36,431 --> 00:06:37,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>what you wanted</b></font>

89
00:06:38,031 --> 00:06:39,631
<font color="#ffff00"><b>is not an ordinary house.</b></font>

90
00:06:41,071 --> 00:06:43,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You wanted a dream.</b></font>

91
00:06:45,751 --> 00:06:48,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He spent all his time with Ding Qi</b></font>

92
00:06:49,591 --> 00:06:51,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>so that he can give you this surprise</b></font>

93
00:06:51,671 --> 00:06:52,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>on your birthday.</b></font>

94
00:06:53,951 --> 00:06:56,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He said this would make you really happy.</b></font>

95
00:06:57,871 --> 00:06:59,191
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You've always been</b></font>

96
00:06:59,791 --> 00:07:01,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>his most cherished person.</b></font>

97
00:07:06,671 --> 00:07:07,911
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm really such a bad person.</b></font>

98
00:07:09,831 --> 00:07:10,711
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Caina.</b></font>

99
00:07:11,471 --> 00:07:13,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You should be honest with yourself.</b></font>

100
00:07:14,631 --> 00:07:16,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even though you've been resisting it,</b></font>

101
00:07:16,751 --> 00:07:17,711
<font color="#ffff00"><b>but you've always loved</b></font>

102
00:07:18,631 --> 00:07:19,911
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Ye Mingchuan.</b></font>

103
00:07:23,071 --> 00:07:23,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Yes.</b></font>

104
00:07:26,071 --> 00:07:27,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I wasn't confident.</b></font>

105
00:07:28,631 --> 00:07:29,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I was insecure.</b></font>

106
00:07:30,591 --> 00:07:31,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's all my fault.</b></font>

107
00:07:34,311 --> 00:07:36,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm a fool who doesn't know how to love.</b></font>

108
00:07:42,471 --> 00:07:43,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Meizuo.</b></font>

109
00:07:44,551 --> 00:07:46,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why are you telling me this?</b></font>

110
00:07:46,711 --> 00:07:48,031
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't you hate him?</b></font>

111
00:07:48,911 --> 00:07:49,911
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I do.</b></font>

112
00:07:51,751 --> 00:07:52,631
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But</b></font>

113
00:07:54,311 --> 00:07:55,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I like you.</b></font>

114
00:08:02,671 --> 00:08:03,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I always thought that...</b></font>

115
00:08:05,071 --> 00:08:06,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b>to make someone fall in love with you,</b></font>

116
00:08:08,071 --> 00:08:09,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you have to make her smile.</b></font>

117
00:08:14,111 --> 00:08:16,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I've learned</b></font>

118
00:08:18,591 --> 00:08:20,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>that when you really love someone,</b></font>

119
00:08:21,751 --> 00:08:22,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you'd unconsciously</b></font>

120
00:08:24,071 --> 00:08:25,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>cry because of her.</b></font>

121
00:08:30,231 --> 00:08:31,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Meizuo.</b></font>

122
00:08:32,311 --> 00:08:34,031
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You've done so much for me.</b></font>

123
00:08:36,191 --> 00:08:37,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't want you to feel miserable.</b></font>

124
00:08:39,511 --> 00:08:40,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't worry.</b></font>

125
00:08:41,191 --> 00:08:43,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Youngsters like us fall in love</b></font>

126
00:08:44,151 --> 00:08:45,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and move on.</b></font>

127
00:08:45,951 --> 00:08:47,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We're honest with how we feel.</b></font>

128
00:08:49,031 --> 00:08:50,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But that guy</b></font>

129
00:08:51,351 --> 00:08:52,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>really likes you.</b></font>

130
00:08:54,351 --> 00:08:55,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He just couldn't tell you.</b></font>

131
00:08:58,231 --> 00:09:00,631
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop wasting time.</b></font>

132
00:09:01,471 --> 00:09:02,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When he leaves,</b></font>

133
00:09:03,471 --> 00:09:05,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you might not see him anymore.</b></font>

134
00:09:08,551 --> 00:09:09,471
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Caina.</b></font>

135
00:09:10,071 --> 00:09:11,191
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This tree house is here.</b></font>

136
00:09:12,471 --> 00:09:14,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But Mr. Coconut is leaving.</b></font>

137
00:09:14,871 --> 00:09:16,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Aren't you going after him?</b></font>

138
00:09:19,871 --> 00:09:21,471
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you, Meizuo.</b></font>

139
00:09:22,511 --> 00:09:23,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

140
00:10:07,991 --> 00:10:08,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But before I go,</b></font>

141
00:10:10,551 --> 00:10:12,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I hope you can give something to her.</b></font>

142
00:10:19,871 --> 00:10:21,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>TREE HOUSE DESIGN</b></font>

143
00:10:26,791 --> 00:10:28,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I spent a lot of time preparing
this tree house for her.</b></font>

144
00:10:29,911 --> 00:10:31,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's located in her backyard.</b></font>

145
00:10:33,511 --> 00:10:34,471
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She told me</b></font>

146
00:10:35,311 --> 00:10:37,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>that she doesn't like to stay
in a house like a cage.</b></font>

147
00:10:38,751 --> 00:10:39,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>She likes tree houses.</b></font>

148
00:10:41,191 --> 00:10:43,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When I'm in the house,</b></font>

149
00:10:44,271 --> 00:10:45,511
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm a like a bird</b></font>

150
00:10:45,951 --> 00:10:47,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>in a cage.</b></font>

151
00:10:49,111 --> 00:10:49,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is that so?</b></font>

152
00:10:50,751 --> 00:10:51,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You feel that way too?</b></font>

153
00:10:54,231 --> 00:10:55,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's how I've always felt.</b></font>

154
00:10:56,751 --> 00:11:00,031
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It turns out I'm not the only one
who feels that way.</b></font>

155
00:11:05,111 --> 00:11:08,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I really like the tree houses
in fairy tales.</b></font>

156
00:11:17,351 --> 00:11:18,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I know this is insignificant.</i></b></font>

157
00:11:20,551 --> 00:11:21,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Initially,</i></b></font>

158
00:11:21,711 --> 00:11:23,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I wanted to give it to her as a surprise.</i></b></font>

159
00:11:27,631 --> 00:11:28,711
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>The two must overlap.</i></b></font>

160
00:11:29,271 --> 00:11:31,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The living room in front,
bedroom at the back.</b></font>

161
00:11:31,271 --> 00:11:32,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Overlap.
-Yes.</b></font>

162
00:11:32,951 --> 00:11:34,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then a French window in the middle.</b></font>

163
00:11:34,831 --> 00:11:36,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The living room in front,
bedroom at the back.</b></font>

164
00:11:37,271 --> 00:11:38,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>This tree here...</b></font>

165
00:12:17,391 --> 00:12:18,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It has an oval shape.</b></font>

166
00:12:19,111 --> 00:12:21,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It's a tree house with two eggs
overlapping together.</b></font>

167
00:12:22,591 --> 00:12:24,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Overlapping together.
-Yes.</b></font>

168
00:12:27,231 --> 00:12:29,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Please give this to her on my behalf.</b></font>

169
00:12:32,991 --> 00:12:34,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I hope you can always make her happy.</b></font>

170
00:13:16,551 --> 00:13:17,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where is he?</b></font>

171
00:13:17,991 --> 00:13:19,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He already left.</b></font>

172
00:13:19,311 --> 00:13:20,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He left?</b></font>

173
00:13:20,271 --> 00:13:21,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where did he go?</b></font>

174
00:13:21,871 --> 00:13:24,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He confirmed his next project.</b></font>

175
00:13:24,711 --> 00:13:25,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>He went to the States.</b></font>

176
00:14:41,751 --> 00:14:43,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How can you leave?</b></font>

177
00:14:44,231 --> 00:14:46,511
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're leaving
without finishing the renovation.</b></font>

178
00:14:47,231 --> 00:14:48,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If my dad doesn't like it,</b></font>

179
00:14:49,391 --> 00:14:50,711
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I have to go back to the States.</b></font>

180
00:14:51,031 --> 00:14:52,511
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But I want to stay in Shanghai.</b></font>

181
00:14:52,591 --> 00:14:55,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How can you be so irresponsible?</b></font>

182
00:14:57,151 --> 00:14:58,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm not leaving.</b></font>

183
00:14:59,791 --> 00:15:01,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But why are you here at the airport?</b></font>

184
00:15:05,951 --> 00:15:07,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm waiting for someone</b></font>

185
00:15:07,631 --> 00:15:08,631
<font color="#ffff00"><b>to travel with me.</b></font>

186
00:15:23,311 --> 00:15:25,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How did you know I'd be here?</b></font>

187
00:15:28,391 --> 00:15:29,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't know.</b></font>

188
00:15:31,151 --> 00:15:32,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Just like before.</b></font>

189
00:15:32,951 --> 00:15:35,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I thought you liked me,
but you disappeared.</b></font>

190
00:15:37,111 --> 00:15:38,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I really don't know what you'll do.</b></font>

191
00:15:39,391 --> 00:15:42,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm just doing whatever I can.</b></font>

192
00:15:43,271 --> 00:15:44,511
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then I can only wait.</b></font>

193
00:15:53,791 --> 00:15:55,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How long will you keep waiting for me?</b></font>

194
00:16:00,631 --> 00:16:01,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Until that one day</b></font>

195
00:16:03,991 --> 00:16:05,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you'll feel that being with me</b></font>

196
00:16:07,951 --> 00:16:08,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>would make you happy.</b></font>

