<font color="#ffff00"><b>Maybe I'm just exhausted.</b></font>

385
00:30:16,631 --> 00:30:17,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>When I was with him,</b></font>

386
00:30:19,231 --> 00:30:21,031
<font color="#ffff00"><b>it felt like things always went wrong.</b></font>

387
00:30:22,351 --> 00:30:23,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Can you really forget him?</b></font>

388
00:30:29,831 --> 00:30:31,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How do I put it?</b></font>

389
00:30:33,431 --> 00:30:35,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>There were many times</b></font>

390
00:30:35,871 --> 00:30:37,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>when I realized I fell in love with him.</b></font>

391
00:30:38,671 --> 00:30:39,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then, get back together.</b></font>

392
00:30:40,631 --> 00:30:43,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Falling in love is the best gift
in this world.</b></font>

393
00:30:43,511 --> 00:30:45,271
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Many people want to, but they can't.</b></font>

394
00:30:47,391 --> 00:30:49,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>But when I first knew him,</b></font>

395
00:30:50,151 --> 00:30:52,511
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I definitely, completely</b></font>

396
00:30:52,591 --> 00:30:53,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>didn't like him at all.</b></font>

397
00:30:54,511 --> 00:30:56,911
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-I even hated him.
-That was before.</b></font>

398
00:31:04,071 --> 00:31:05,631
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then I'll go back to the way it was.</b></font>

399
00:31:11,751 --> 00:31:15,271
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I definitely, completely
don't like him at all!</b></font>

400
00:31:18,951 --> 00:31:20,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Now I'm back to square one.</b></font>

401
00:31:23,111 --> 00:31:24,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>As if nothing happened.</b></font>

402
00:31:41,991 --> 00:31:44,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-What are you doing?
-I want to tell you something. Follow me.</b></font>

403
00:31:46,711 --> 00:31:47,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let go of me.</b></font>

404
00:32:03,151 --> 00:32:04,911
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't you have something to tell me?</b></font>

405
00:32:05,871 --> 00:32:08,471
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you have nothing to say,
then I'll leave.</b></font>

406
00:32:09,831 --> 00:32:11,271
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Can't you stay with me for a while?</b></font>

407
00:32:16,431 --> 00:32:18,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you hate it when I'm around?</b></font>

408
00:32:19,591 --> 00:32:20,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's not what I meant.</b></font>

409
00:32:24,031 --> 00:32:25,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You suddenly disappeared</b></font>

410
00:32:25,831 --> 00:32:28,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and hid in the fishing village
to sell squid. What were you thinking?</b></font>

411
00:32:31,071 --> 00:32:34,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b>The fishing village was nice.
It was relaxing there.</b></font>

412
00:32:34,791 --> 00:32:36,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I had squid and went
to the beach every day.</b></font>

413
00:32:37,151 --> 00:32:38,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It was like a vacation.</b></font>

414
00:32:38,391 --> 00:32:39,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-You don't know how happy--
-Shancai.</b></font>

415
00:32:40,311 --> 00:32:41,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You're so disappointing.</b></font>

416
00:32:46,711 --> 00:32:48,511
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Every time I want to have a serious talk,</b></font>

417
00:32:49,591 --> 00:32:50,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you either talk nonsense</b></font>

418
00:32:51,311 --> 00:32:53,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>or hide or sleep.</b></font>

419
00:32:53,231 --> 00:32:54,911
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you know how to be honest?</b></font>

420
00:32:56,671 --> 00:32:57,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Daoming Si.</b></font>

421
00:32:59,391 --> 00:33:02,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-It's not that I don't know--
-If you can honestly face your feelings,</b></font>

422
00:33:02,911 --> 00:33:05,911
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I don't need to be like a clown
getting played by you!</b></font>

423
00:33:06,471 --> 00:33:08,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I can't only think about my own happiness</b></font>

424
00:33:09,271 --> 00:33:10,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and not care about others.</b></font>

425
00:33:10,751 --> 00:33:13,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If Qinghe and Xiaoyou were not in trouble,</b></font>

426
00:33:13,711 --> 00:33:15,711
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I wouldn't have had to go
to the fishing village.</b></font>

427
00:33:16,431 --> 00:33:17,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>That's just an excuse.</b></font>

428
00:33:17,391 --> 00:33:19,471
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You always have a lot of excuses!</b></font>

429
00:33:19,831 --> 00:33:21,191
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I think I really am that stupid.</b></font>

430
00:33:21,271 --> 00:33:22,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I've had enough!</b></font>

431
00:33:38,151 --> 00:33:39,471
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you think I want</b></font>

432
00:33:40,471 --> 00:33:41,471
<font color="#ffff00"><b>to wander around</b></font>

433
00:33:42,671 --> 00:33:43,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and struggle like this?</b></font>

434
00:33:50,151 --> 00:33:51,031
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Daoming Si.</b></font>

435
00:33:52,471 --> 00:33:54,271
<font color="#ffff00"><b>-Actually, I--
-Don't cry.</b></font>

436
00:33:56,471 --> 00:33:57,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even if you cry,</b></font>

437
00:34:00,151 --> 00:34:01,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I won't do anything for you anymore.</b></font>

438
00:34:03,911 --> 00:34:04,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Also,</b></font>

439
00:34:06,311 --> 00:34:07,631
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you don't need to run away</b></font>

440
00:34:08,471 --> 00:34:09,871
<font color="#ffff00"><b>when you see me in school anymore.</b></font>

441
00:34:11,031 --> 00:34:12,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>We have nothing to do
with each other anymore.</b></font>

442
00:34:14,751 --> 00:34:15,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Just like strangers.</b></font>

443
00:34:18,711 --> 00:34:19,911
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let's end it today.</b></font>

444
00:34:22,711 --> 00:34:23,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Goodbye.</b></font>

445
00:34:28,311 --> 00:34:29,471
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Daoming Si!</b></font>

446
00:35:03,391 --> 00:35:04,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Since that's the case...</b></font>

447
00:35:14,671 --> 00:35:16,191
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Here's the meteor necklace</b></font>

448
00:35:17,831 --> 00:35:18,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you gave me.</b></font>

449
00:37:13,271 --> 00:37:15,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Daoming Si, I like you.</i></b></font>

450
00:37:15,951 --> 00:37:17,271
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I really like you.</i></b></font>

451
00:37:18,591 --> 00:37:20,191
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>There was a moment earlier</i></b></font>

452
00:37:20,791 --> 00:37:23,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>when I almost told you that.</i></b></font>

453
00:37:24,871 --> 00:37:26,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I almost destroyed my friends' families.</i></b></font>

454
00:37:26,871 --> 00:37:29,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I almost threw away my pride
and self-respect!</i></b></font>

455
00:37:29,311 --> 00:37:31,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I almost threw everything away
and confessed to you.</i></b></font>

456
00:37:32,791 --> 00:37:33,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>I really...</i></b></font>

457
00:37:35,151 --> 00:37:36,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>almost confessed my feelings.</i></b></font>

458
00:37:45,271 --> 00:37:46,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, what are you doing?</b></font>

459
00:37:49,991 --> 00:37:51,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai, come up here.</b></font>

460
00:37:53,271 --> 00:37:54,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lei.</b></font>

461
00:37:54,231 --> 00:37:56,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm begging you. Help me find it.</b></font>

462
00:37:56,311 --> 00:37:58,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Please come here and help me
find it, okay?</b></font>

463
00:37:59,031 --> 00:38:00,031
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you looking for?</b></font>

464
00:38:19,871 --> 00:38:20,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Stop it.</b></font>

465
00:38:20,991 --> 00:38:23,271
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even if it's something very meaningful,
it's gone now.</b></font>

466
00:38:24,631 --> 00:38:25,871
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No! I want to find it!</b></font>

467
00:38:26,511 --> 00:38:27,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I have to find it!</b></font>

468
00:38:29,471 --> 00:38:30,711
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Why can't I find it?</b></font>

469
00:38:31,911 --> 00:38:33,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I want to find it!</b></font>

470
00:38:35,511 --> 00:38:37,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Where is it?</b></font>

471
00:39:04,431 --> 00:39:05,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is this the one?</b></font>

472
00:39:05,951 --> 00:39:07,591
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Is this what you're looking for?</b></font>

473
00:39:17,871 --> 00:39:19,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Now, I know how it feels like
to love someone.</i></b></font>

474
00:39:21,631 --> 00:39:23,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>Whatever you do,</i></b></font>

475
00:39:23,951 --> 00:39:26,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>you can't turn away from your feelings.</i></b></font>

476
00:39:26,831 --> 00:39:29,711
<font color="#ffff00"><b><i>You can't stop yourself from loving him.</i></b></font>

477
00:40:32,351 --> 00:40:34,711
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, why are you drinking so much?</b></font>

478
00:40:34,791 --> 00:40:35,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's wrong?</b></font>

479
00:40:36,271 --> 00:40:38,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm happy. Can't I drink to celebrate?</b></font>

480
00:40:38,511 --> 00:40:39,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Celebrate?</b></font>

481
00:40:39,951 --> 00:40:41,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What are you celebrating?</b></font>

482
00:40:42,551 --> 00:40:44,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>To celebrate that Lei and Shancai</b></font>

483
00:40:44,751 --> 00:40:45,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>are officially dating.</b></font>

484
00:40:47,991 --> 00:40:49,031
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How is that possible?</b></font>

485
00:40:49,111 --> 00:40:50,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you drunk?</b></font>

486
00:40:50,911 --> 00:40:51,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No.</b></font>

487
00:40:52,391 --> 00:40:53,791
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm very sober.</b></font>

488
00:40:54,351 --> 00:40:55,191
<font color="#ffff00"><b>After all this time,</b></font>

489
00:40:55,791 --> 00:40:57,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I'm the most sober now.</b></font>

490
00:41:00,471 --> 00:41:01,551
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How could that happen?</b></font>

491
00:41:02,191 --> 00:41:03,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Has Lei already decided?</b></font>

492
00:41:08,911 --> 00:41:09,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What's your plan?</b></font>

493
00:41:13,191 --> 00:41:14,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>What do you mean?</b></font>

494
00:41:14,991 --> 00:41:16,271
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I wish them well, of course.</b></font>

495
00:41:17,351 --> 00:41:19,271
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't you think this is great?</b></font>

496
00:41:19,911 --> 00:41:21,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, cut it out.</b></font>

497
00:41:21,351 --> 00:41:22,871
<font color="#ffff00"><b>How can you not care at all?</b></font>

498
00:41:23,791 --> 00:41:26,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do you want to kick Lei
out of F4 like before?</b></font>

499
00:41:27,631 --> 00:41:29,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>No. Why would I do that?</b></font>

500
00:41:30,551 --> 00:41:31,511
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Lei said</b></font>

501
00:41:31,911 --> 00:41:33,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I should wish him well,</b></font>

502
00:41:34,271 --> 00:41:36,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b>just like he did before.</b></font>

503
00:41:38,311 --> 00:41:39,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, this is not you.</b></font>

504
00:41:40,031 --> 00:41:41,351
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Listen carefully.</b></font>

505
00:41:41,431 --> 00:41:43,031
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you really give her up this time,</b></font>

506
00:41:43,111 --> 00:41:45,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>you might not have a chance anymore.</b></font>

507
00:41:45,871 --> 00:41:47,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>And that's Lei.</b></font>

508
00:41:47,911 --> 00:41:49,151
<font color="#ffff00"><b>It'll be more complicated now.</b></font>

509
00:41:50,431 --> 00:41:53,511
<font color="#ffff00"><b>If you regret it later,
you'll lose both friendship and love.</b></font>

510
00:41:54,071 --> 00:41:55,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Have you thought it out?</b></font>

511
00:41:55,951 --> 00:41:57,431
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Shancai and I are done.</b></font>

512
00:42:01,191 --> 00:42:03,951
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Are you saying you don't care
who Shancai will be seeing?</b></font>

513
00:42:04,511 --> 00:42:05,711
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Of course!</b></font>

514
00:42:07,151 --> 00:42:09,391
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Come on. Let's toast for Lei!</b></font>

515
00:42:17,711 --> 00:42:18,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si, you...</b></font>

516
00:42:28,391 --> 00:42:31,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Even if it's not necessary,
I still think I should tell you.</b></font>

517
00:42:32,351 --> 00:42:34,471
<font color="#ffff00"><b>I value F4's friendship.</b></font>

518
00:42:35,631 --> 00:42:38,111
<font color="#ffff00"><b>So please wish me well.</b></font>

519
00:42:41,911 --> 00:42:44,671
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Or would you rather have a fight with me?</b></font>

520
00:42:45,991 --> 00:42:46,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Then let's fight.</b></font>

521
00:42:48,911 --> 00:42:49,991
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let me tell you again.</b></font>

522
00:42:51,071 --> 00:42:53,231
<font color="#ffff00"><b>You don't have to tell me
what you want to do.</b></font>

523
00:42:55,991 --> 00:42:57,071
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Do whatever you want.</b></font>

524
00:42:58,791 --> 00:42:59,631
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si.</b></font>

525
00:43:00,871 --> 00:43:02,311
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Let me take care of Shancai.</b></font>

526
00:43:16,391 --> 00:43:19,831
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Don't you think
they're actually quite a match?</b></font>

527
00:43:21,351 --> 00:43:22,511
<font color="#ffff00"><b>A stupid girl...</b></font>

528
00:43:23,111 --> 00:43:25,511
<font color="#ffff00"><b>and a sleepyhead who sleeps all the time.</b></font>

529
00:43:27,911 --> 00:43:28,751
<font color="#ffff00"><b>Si.</b></font>

